  },
  "columnSpan": {
    "mobile": {
      "b-kicker": "all",
      "b-intro": "all"
    },
    "desktop": {
      "b-kicker": "all",
      "b-intro": "all"
    }
  },
  "elementOrder": ["b-kicker", "b-intro", "b-t1", "b-t2", "b-t3", "b-t4"],
  "definitions": {
    "b-kicker": {
      "type": "elementHeading",
      "level": 6,
      "text": "LATENCY THRESHOLDS",
      "align": "left",
      "width": "hug",
      "height": "hug"
    },
    "b-intro": {
      "type": "elementBody",
      "level": 4,
      "text": "Following Miller's (1968) three response-time limits and updated with Doherty's 400ms threshold for flow, four latency bands define the design problem space.",
      "align": "left",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "width": "100%",
      "height": "hug",
      "wordWrap": true,
      "marginBottom": "0.25rem"
    },
    "b-t1": {
      "type": "elementRichText",
      "content": "### 0 – 100ms\n\n**Instantaneous**\n\nUser perceives the response as a direct effect of their action. No feedback required. Any visible delay reads as system error.\n\nDesign: no spinner, no skeleton — just immediate visual change.",
      "level": 4,
      "align": "left",
      "width": "100%",
      "height": "hug",
      "wordWrap": true,
      "motionTiming": {
        "entrancePreset": "slideUp",
        "viewport": {
          "amount": 0.2
        },
        "entranceMotion": {
          "transition": {
            "duration": 0.4,
            "delay": 0
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "b-t2": {
      "type": "elementRichText",
      "content": "### 100 – 400ms\n\n**Responsive**\n\nUser perceives the response as prompt. A subtle transition is appropriate to communicate state change. Doherty Threshold: below 400ms sustains flow.\n\nDesign: micro-animation; no progress indicator.",
      "level": 4,
      "align": "left",
      "width": "100%",
      "height": "hug",
      "wordWrap": true,
      "motionTiming": {
        "entrancePreset": "slideUp",
        "viewport": {
          "amount": 0.2
        },
        "entranceMotion": {
          "transition": {
            "duration": 0.4,
            "delay": 0.07
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "b-t3": {
      "type": "elementRichText",
      "content": "### 400ms – 1s\n\n**Noticeable**\n\nUser is aware of waiting. A spinner or skeleton prevents abandonment. Perceived duration is malleable — progress cues compress it.\n\nDesign: skeleton screens, optimistic UI, or animated placeholders.",
      "level": 4,
      "align": "left",
      "width": "100%",
      "height": "hug",
      "wordWrap": true,
      "motionTiming": {
        "entrancePreset": "slideUp",
        "viewport": {
          "amount": 0.2
        },
        "entranceMotion": {
          "transition": {
            "duration": 0.4,
            "delay": 0.14
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "b-t4": {
      "type": "elementRichText",
      "content": "### 1s+\n\n**Disruptive**\n\nUser's mental model of the task is interrupted. Context switching begins above 1s. Above 10s, they will likely abandon.\n\nDesign: background processing + notification on completion; break the wait.",
      "level": 4,
      "align": "left",
      "width": "100%",
      "height": "hug",
      "wordWrap": true,
      "motionTiming": {
        "entrancePreset": "slideUp",
        "viewport": {
          "amount": 0.2
        },
        "entranceMotion": {
          "transition": {
            "duration": 0.4,
            "delay": 0.21
          }
        }
      }
    }
  },
  "gridMode": {
    "mobile": "columns",
    "desktop": "grid"
  },
  "gridDebug": false,
  "columnAssignments": {
    "mobile": {
      "b-kicker": 0,
      "b-intro": 0,
      "b-t1": 0,
      "b-t2": 0,
